1.演者の初期配置
2.演出開始
Girl Amina: Luid! Luid, where are you!?

Girl Amina: 'Please come out! I'll use my big sister
privileges, so come out!'

Boy Luid: 'It's been a while since I heard that, Amina big
sister privilege activated.'
Girl Amina: Regarding Lady Caron's marriage...

Boy Luid: 'There are circumstances with my mother too, so I
don't just want to wait, I want to be of help to her.'

Girl Amina: No way... Are you going to war!? Absolutely not,
you're not even of age for military service yet, right!?

Boy Luid: 'I know that, so I have to become stronger by the
time I reach that age.'

Boy Luid: 'This is something even Amina big sister's orders
can't make me obey, it's my strong will.'
Girl Amina: 'Luid...'

The marriage of King Agnos and Caron. Rumors of war
starting. This not only shocks Luid, but also Amina. The
passage of time is pulling Caron away from Luid...

It meant that such a sweet idea had crumbled. Since the
marriage, Amina had begun to lose control over Luid.

Amina started training with Luid. This was initially to keep
an eye on Luid's reckless behavior, but it was also driven
by her pure desire to be with him, even if just for a little
while.

The precious days spent training with Luid. Ironically, it
would prove useful when entering the Imperial Dark Division
as his bodyguard.
イベント終了用

1.演者の初期配置
2.演出開始
Maid Amina: Lloyd... You're here again today, aren't you?

Maid Amina: Now, let's go back home and take a rest, shall
we? I'll make the vegetable soup that Lloyd likes.

Young Lloyd: I wonder if Mother... has come back. After all,
Lord Agnos has passed away, so she should be all alone.
Young Lloyd: I have to go and pick her up...

Maid Amina: First, let's take a rest. My mother is also
worried about Lloyd.
Maid Amina: ...Caron-sama will never come back here again.
Maid Amina: Lloyd, you understand, don't you?
00_Black

After returning from the battlefield and several months
passing, Lloyd began to gradually understand and accept the
reality surrounding him. This change was also brought about
by the devoted actions of Amina.

Splitting firewood, hunting, helping with laundry... such
ordinary things gradually but surely loosened the chains of
Lloyd's mother, who bound him.

It might be good to live here with Amina and the others...
Maybe it's time to give up on my mother... Just as I started
thinking that, a letter arrived for Lloyd from the palace.
The sender was his mother, Caron.
